Value:
An Armory where various weaponry used by Nikkes is stored.
You can always find Nikkes from Absolute here.

A workspace for the Commander.
You can always find Nikkes from Counters here.

A Radio Tower that transmits and receives radio waves from the Ark.
You can always find Nikkes from Protocol here.

A Cafe in the Outpost that specializes in vending machine coffee.
You can always find Nikkes from Cafe Sweety here.

A Bulletin Board where dispatch missions are posted.
You can find odd jobs for Nikkes on it.

A Hospital that treats Nikkes, humans, and everything in between.
You can always find Nikkes from Seraphim here.
A Shopping Mall packed to the gills with goods that cater to all shopaholics' needs. You can always find Nikkes from Talentum here.

A Fitness Club with various types of recreational sports facilities.
You can always find Nikkes from Nepenthe here.

A Police Station that is responsible for maintaining public security in the Outpost.
You can always find Nikkes from A.C.P.U. here.

A Trendy Bar where you can make small talk over a few cocktails.
Non-alcoholic drinks are also available for younger Nikkes.
You can always find Nikkes from Exotic here.
A luxury hotel that welcomes all Nikkes.

An observation station that detects enemies approaching the Outpost.
You can always find Nikkes from the Scouts here.

A Workshop that churns out one item after another.
You can always find Nikkes from Mighty Tools here.

It hasn't been linked to the Ark and the surface yet.
You can find Nikkes from Infinity Rail here.

An Elevator that goes back and forth between the surface, the Outpost, and the Ark.
However, it breaks down quite often.

A research facility that has made a name for itself by sharing the battle data of the most combat-hardened Nikkes.
It'll be no surprise if this is the birthplace of a new generation of fighters.

A research facility that focuses on improving combat power by using surplus Nikke parts.
To them, even the smallest parts are held in high regard.

A research facility that educates Nikkes on combat tactics.
The instructors are strict, but the passion that courses through their classes is as impressive as their intensity.
A research facility where Commanders can receive various benefits by completing the list of achievements.

A cafe full of girlish charm. It seems that some maids work here.
It's got a small and cozy atmosphere.

A Toy Store filled with various intriguing toys.
A huge eye-catching toy is also displayed above the store.
You can always find Nikkes from the Carronades here.

An enormous Generator.
You can always find Nikkes from Matis here.

A library for broadening one's horizon.
You can always find Nikkes from Recall & Release and M.M.R. here.

A grand theater magnificent as an opera house.
You can always find Nikkes from Master Hand and Prima Donna here.

A suspicious-looking club.
You can always find Nikkes from Wardress here.

An immaculately maintained court, the symbol of justice and law.
You can always find Nikkes from Triangle here.

A Church where one worships and prays in faith.
You can always find Nikkes from Extrinsic here.

A luxurious clothing store. 
You can always find Nikkes from Unlimited here.

A statue of Nike, the legendary Goddess of Victory.
You can always find Nikkes from Pioneer here.

A statue of wings.
You can always find Nikkes from Inherit here.

A busy and noisy Amusement Park. 
With just a simple glance, the large Ferris wheel can impress everyone.
A flower park where blossoms are dancing in the wind.

The area where guests are received.
While a bit shabby, it gets the job done.
